{"build_type":"library","description":"Concise lens: walk the function_definitions members as a linked list of json-tree-node structs (node = first child, follow .next) and, for each, add {fn_name: concise(fn)} to fns_out. Native .child/.next traversal — no fetch_member_residing_within_sequence index counting (that re-walks the list each step, O(n^2), and was the source of a NULL-deref on larger inputs). Caller passes the first child (function_definitions.child); 0 means no functions. Tail-recursive on .next. Reuses vw_one_function, attach_named_member_inside_mapping.","module_name":"render-concise-representation-across-functions","package_name":"render-concise-representation-across-functions","function_definitions":{"render-concise-representation-across-functions":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"node","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"fns_out","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"node"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"key","base":"node","dest":"fn_name"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"render-concise-single-function-definition","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"node"}],"result_assignment_variable":"fn_out","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"attach-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"fns_out"},{"kind":"var","value":"fn_name"},{"kind":"var","value":"fn_out"}]},{"instruction_type":"field_read","struct":"json-tree-node","field":"next","base":"node","dest":"nxt"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"render-concise-representation-across-functions","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"nxt"},{"kind":"var","value":"fns_out"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}